, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrap_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrap_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrap_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrap_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>红毯上与<em>NME</em>进行了交谈，分享了他们对爱尔兰民谣乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lankum">Lankum</a>的热爱，并预告了将于下周发行的新歌。查看上面的完整采访。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/jockstrap-interview-i-love-you-jennifer-b-debut-album-radar-3303259">认识一下 Jockstrap：2022 年最伟大的首张专辑之一背后的富有远见的二人组</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（9 月 7 日）在 Hammersmith&#39;s Eventim Apollo 演出之前，由 Georgia Ellery 和 Taylor Skye 组成的二人组接受了<em>NME</em>采访，回顾了人们对新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709">《I Love You Jennifer B》</a>和即将推出的歌曲的反应。已经在地平线上。</p><p>虽然对曲目的任何具体细节严格保密，但二人确实表示，自 2016 年成立以来，他们对自己的艺术选择变得更加“自信”，并且更愿意与其他艺术家合作。</p><p>他们解释说，这将出现在下周发行的一首新歌中，其中有一位神秘嘉宾。 “我们有一位明星加入……我不能告诉你是谁，”埃勒里开玩笑说，而斯凯则提供了另一个关于这位艺术家可能是谁的暗示，他说：“新一代。”这是新一代的艺术家……”</p><p>在采访的其他地方，这对伦敦二人组回顾了他们最近的一系列现场表演中粉丝们压倒性的积极反应，并解释了今年早些时候在他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/blur-live-in-london-wembley-setlist-photos-review-3466214">规模宏大的温布利表演</a>中为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a>开场的感觉。 </p><figure id="attachment_3494854" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3494854" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3494854" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrapv2_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="乔治亚·埃勒里和泰勒·斯凯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrapv2_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrapv2_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrapv2_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrapv2_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrapv2_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_jockstrapv2_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3494854" class="wp-caption-text"> Jockstrap 的 Georgia Ellery 和 Taylor Skye 出席 2023 年 9 月 7 日在伦敦 Eventim Apollo 举行的 2023 年水星奖颁奖典礼 图片来源：JMEnternational/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “过去一年的反应非常好。我们非常幸运。有一些伟大的节日，人们一起唱歌。不能要求更多了，”埃勒里开始说道。 “他们收到了备忘录。他们知道该做什么，那就是玩得很开心。唱歌。舞蹈。吻。哭…”</p><p>斯凯同意了，并继续反思他们如何在最近与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/damon-albarn">达蒙·阿尔本</a>和公司一起举办的演出中找到了英伦流行乐迷的观众。“我们赢得了他们的支持，是的。他们很喜欢它！”他告诉<em>《NME》</em> ，而埃勒里补充说，他们也在演出结束时“跪下来向他们鞠躬”。</p><p> “那里只有大约 100 人，但这 100 人……”斯凯继续说道。 “我们当天很早就开始比赛，但仍然非常好。这就像在一场比赛中一样，在这个疯狂的体育场里比赛感觉很奇怪！”</p><p>说到与巨星一起演奏，这对流行艺术二人组还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave">戴夫</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/weyes-blood">韦耶斯·布拉德</a>列为他们接下来最想合作的两位艺术家，并分享了他们对水星奖入围艺术家兰库姆的喜爱。 </p><figure id="attachment_3475877" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3475877" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3475877" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/LANKUM_MERCURY_2000.jpg" alt="Lankum 荣获 2023 年水星奖。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/LANKUM_MERCURY_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/LANKUM_MERCURY_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/LANKUM_MERCURY_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/LANKUM_MERCURY_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/LANKUM_MERCURY_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/LANKUM_MERCURY_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3475877" class="wp-caption-text">来自 Lankum 的 Daragh Lynch、Ian Lynch 和 Cormac MacDiarmada 出席 2023 年水星奖颁奖典礼（摄影：JMEnternational/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> “我们是 Lankum 的新手，他们给我们留下了深刻的印象，”当被问及他们最近几个月喜欢哪些专辑时，Skye 解释道。 “我们正在慢慢地尝试，因为这是一种非常不寻常的音乐，我们正在慢慢地[探索]，”他补充道。</p><p>埃勒里对此表示同意，并确认虽然她还没有“听完整张专辑”，但迄今为止她听到的部分都“令人惊叹”。</p><p>除了 Jockstrap 和 Lankum 之外，其他入围今年水星奖的艺术家还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">Loyle Carner</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/RAYE">Raye</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-fathers">Young Fathers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ARCTIC-MONKEYS">Arctic Monkeys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shygirl">Shygirl</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/JESSIE-WARE">Jessie Ware</a> 。</p><p>然而，英国爵士乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-win-the-2023-mercury-prize-for-where-im-meant-to-be-3494841">获得了令人垂涎的奖项</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-on-their-impact-on-the-jazz-scene-and-plans-to-celebrate-their-mercury-prize-win-3495161">与 NME 讨论了在享有盛誉的颁奖典礼上代表爵士乐界意味着什么</a>。</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jockstrap-tease-new-collaborative-single-and-share-love-of-irish-folk-band-lankum-3495281">Jockstrap 预告了新的合作单曲并分享了对爱尔兰民谣乐队 Lankum 的热爱，该单曲</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 “Rust”机载更新将热气球变成飞行堡垒https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/rust-airborne-update-turns-hot-air-balloons-into-flying-fortresses-3495263?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rust-airborne-update-turns-hot-air-balloons-into-flying-fortressesImogen Donovan Fri, 08 Sep 2023 15:56:18 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS4Xbox One https://www.nme.com/?p=3495263 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Keep watching the skies</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/rust-airborne-update-turns-hot-air-balloons-into-flying-fortresses-3495263">&#39;Rust&#39; Airborne update turns hot air balloons into flying fortresses</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The Airborne update for <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/rust"><em>Rust</em></a> has added an attack helicopter, parachutes and armoured hot air balloons to travel through the skies, as well as a homing missile launcher to take enemies out.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/british-racing-greats-a-charity-driven-celebration-of-car-culture-and-gaming-3469412">British Racing Greats: a charity-driven celebration of car culture and gaming</a></strong></li></ul><p> In a <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/252490/view/3669925177429727838" target="_blank" rel="noopener">post</a> to Steam, <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/facepunch-studios">Facepunch Studios</a> showcased everything that the update offers as well as the improvements to the pumpjack and quarry models, hot air balloon fuel consumption and decay, signifiers for unlearnable blueprints, and more.</p><p> There was also a trailer that encouraged the community to wreak chaos with the new aerial additions.看看下面： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="铁锈 - 空气传播" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gTKll4bk968?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <em>Rust</em> &#39;s new attack helicopter, costing 2,250 scrap from the Air Wolf store at the bandit camp, features a pilot and a gunner seat. Players are able to use the turret or HV and incendiary rockets to launch an assault on opponents.</p><p> However, the homing missile launcher has the capability to take this threat out very effectively. Pilots should be aware of a warning lock audio to avoid being hit by the missiles and send out a flare (if available) to disrupt the path of the missile. Homing missiles are craftable, too, for 20 HQM, three metal pipes, one tech trash and one CCTV Camera.</p><p> <em>Rust</em> players will also be able to use parachutes to direct their descent from heights. The parachute does degrade with each use though and a lower quality parachute falls faster, flies forward slower and is harder to manoeuvre with.</p><p> Last but not least, the hot air balloon is now reinforceable with corrugated steel and wood to boost the balloon&#39;s health pool and provide protection from other players. This upgrade is found at the vehicle parts vendor at the bandit camp. </p><figure id="attachment_3495284" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3495284" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3495284" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rust-airborne-update-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3495284" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Rust&#39; Credit: Facepunch Studios</figcaption></figure><p> Additionally, the edges of the world will react differently to players who travel out of bounds. Previously, the player and their vehicle would be destroyed with no notification that they had lost their way. The update now prevents vehicles or boats from exiting the limits of the world with a “force” applied to push the player back to the safe area.</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dark-and-darker"><em>Dark And Darker</em></a> was hit with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-servers-targeted-by-a-titanic-ddos-attack-3495233">a huge distributed denial-of-service (or DDoS) attack</a> , weighing in at over “600 Gbps” according to the developer.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/rust-airborne-update-turns-hot-air-balloons-into-flying-fortresses-3495263">&#39;Rust&#39; Airborne update turns hot air balloons into flying fortresses</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
